ReplicationJson - Class in com.vangav.backend.cassandra.keyspaces_generator.json
ReplicationJson represents a Cassandra keyspace's replication e.g.: - 'class': 'NetworkTopologyStrategy', 'DC1' : 1, 'DC2' : 1 - 'class': 'SimpleStrategy', 'replication_factor' : 1 In production there's only one replication method for a keyspace, support for multiple replication methods per keyspace in vangav_backend is useful for cases like (in dev one wants to deploy a single replica keyspace while in production the keyspace has 2 replicas with two data centers per replica) CQL keyspace Generator generates a script per replica method
